From: Zoltan Herczeg <zherczeg.u-szeged@partner.samsung.com>
Date: Fri, 16 Oct 2020 11:02:36 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Implement proper arguments support (#4289)

- Store arguments in a register when possible
- Create separate arguments object for function argument initializer when necessary

JerryScript-DCO-1.0-Signed-off-by: Zoltan Herczeg zherczeg.u-szeged@partner.samsung.com
